data.description: Your dream home in South Buckhead's Brookwood Hills awaits! Ms. Clean lives in this fabulous 2 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom condo with storage unit (worth up to $10K) in sought-after Brookwood Place - a gated enclave set right in the heart of the city!  Light-filled and airy, the home features engineered hardwoods and tile in the main living areas, a split bedroom floorplan for optimal privacy, powder room, fresh paint and gorgeous contemporary light fixtures, fans and vanity lights. The sunny kitchen has white cabinets, new backsplash, granite countertops, GAS cooktop/stove, stainless appliances and a charming breakfast nook. The oversized bedrooms each have their own bath, and the primary bedroom has two spacious walk-in closets, dual vanities, a separate shower and whirlpool soaking tub and private entry to the large balcony. The living room has a gas fireplace flanked with glass shelving, and a storage cabinet below. The large separate dining room could also serve as a flex/bonus room.  Newer HVAC, brand-new water heater and the roof is only 5 year old.  HOA dues cover internet, cable and gas in addition to the normal concierge, exterior maintenance, common area maintenance/insurance, trash and termite/pest control. Amenities? 24 hour concierge and on-site property manager, pool, business center, exercise room, library, 3-section dog park, car wash area, EV car chargers, two gas grills, an updated guest suite. The building is solid concrete construction and even has a generator for power outages. The interior storage unit is down the hall, and there are two deeded parking spaces. Step out to the best of the city - the Buckhead Beltline, Midtown attractions, gourmet and casual eateries, shopping havens, scenic trails, cultural hubs, top-notch medical facilities, and beautiful walking neighborhoods. Not to mention, you’re minutes away from iconic spots like Piedmont Park, the Fabulous Fox Theatre, and Woodruff Arts Center, with seamless freeway access. Your dream urban lifestyle starts here. Dive into comfort, luxury and convenience
